name: Governor Phil Scott
tweet: (2/3) To call more attention to the good things happening throughout Vermont, and the good people making them happen, I will be highlighting more acts of kindness, selfless service, community spirit and goodwill.

name: Governor Phil Scott
tweet: (1/3) The holiday season is an important time to pause & spend time with family and friends.  As I’ve noted before, at a time when our country feels so divided, it’s important to reflect on what unites us - and the role that this unity plays in making our state a better place.
